**Summary:**
This documentation covers Ampli, a code generation tool that creates type-safe wrappers for Amplitude SDK based on tracking plans in Amplitude Data, including the Ampli CLI for generating wrappers, verifying event instrumentation with `ampli status`, and implementing type-safe event tracking methods.

